/-- At an index `(t,s)`, this process pairs a standard Gaussian vector with
the vectorized rank-one matrix `s ⊗ t`. Its ambient Gaussian vector consists
of `m*n` independent `N(0,1)` entries.

**Lean implementation helper.** -/
def finiteGaussianMatrixChevetProcess {m n : ℕ}
    (T : Finset (EuclideanSpace ℝ (Fin n)))
    (S : Finset (EuclideanSpace ℝ (Fin m))) :
    HDP.RandomProcess (ChevetIndex T S)
      (EuclideanSpace ℝ (Fin m × Fin n)) :=
  rankOneCanonicalGaussianProcess (fun p => p.1.1) (fun p => p.2.1)

